---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Cookie Policy - ReguMe" 
  description="ReguMe's cookie policy and tracking disclosure."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: November 25, 2024</p>

    <h2>What Are Cookies?</h2>

    <p>
      Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit our website. They help 
      websites remember your preferences and provide a better user experience.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Use Cookies</h2>

    <h3>Website Cookies (regume.com)</h3>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Essential Cookies</h4>
      <p>
        <strong>Purpose:</strong> Website functionality and navigation<br/>
        <strong>Required:</strong> Yes (cannot be disabled)
      </p>
      <p>
        These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly. They enable basic 
        features like page navigation and access to secure areas.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Analytics Cookies (Optional)</h4>
      <p>
        <strong>Purpose:</strong> Usage statistics and website improvement<br/>
        <strong>Required:</strong> No
      </p>
      <p>
        If implemented, we may use analytics services (like Google Analytics) to understand how 
        visitors use our website. This helps us improve the user experience.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>You can opt-out</strong> of analytics cookies through your browser settings.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Advertising Cookies</h4>
      <p>
        <strong>We do NOT use advertising cookies.</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        ReguMe does not use cookies for advertising purposes or to track you across other websites.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h3>Mobile App</h3>

    <p>
      The ReguMe mobile app <strong>does NOT use browser cookies</strong>. Instead, we use:
    </p>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Local Storage</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cached data:</strong> Video thumbnails, protocol data (for offline access)</li>
        <li><strong>User preferences:</strong> App settings, display preferences</li>
        <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Secure session tokens</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        This data is stored locally on your device and can be deleted by removing the app.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Analytics SDKs</h4>
      <p>
        We may use analytics tools to track app usage, crashes, and performance. This data helps 
        us improve the app.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>You can opt-out</strong> of analytics in the App settings.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Your Choices</h2>

    <h3>Browser Settings</h3>
    <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Block all cookies:</strong> Prevent all websites from setting cookies</li>
      <li><strong>Block third-party cookies:</strong> Block cookies from external services</li>
      <li><strong>Delete cookies:</strong> Clear existing cookies from your browser</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Note: Blocking essential cookies may limit website functionality.
    </p>

    <h3>App Settings</h3>
    <p>In the ReguMe app:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Go to <strong>Settings â†’ Privacy</strong></li>
      <li>Toggle <strong>"Analytics"</strong> off to opt-out of usage tracking</li>
      <li>Toggle <strong>"Outcome Tracking"</strong> off to opt-out of anonymized health insights</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Do Not Track</h3>
    <p>
      We respect Do Not Track (DNT) browser signals. If you have DNT enabled, we will not track 
      your activity on our website.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

    <p>Our website may load third-party services that use cookies:</p>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Google Analytics (if implemented)</h4>
      <p>
        <strong>Purpose:</strong> Website analytics<br/>
        <strong>Privacy Policy:</strong> <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a><br/>
        <strong>Opt-out:</strong> <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank">Google Analytics Opt-out</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>Hosting Provider</h4>
      <p>
        Our hosting provider may use cookies for functionality and security purposes. Refer to 
        their privacy policy for details.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Cookies We Use</h2>

    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0;">
      <thead>
        <tr style="background: var(--accent); text-align: left;">
          <th style="padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Cookie Name</th>
          <th style="padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Purpose</th>
          <th style="padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Duration</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><code>session_id</code></td>
          <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Website session management</td>
          <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Session (until browser closes)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><code>preferences</code></td>
          <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Remember your settings</td>
          <td style="padding: 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #ddd;">1 year</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-light);">
      <em>Note: Actual cookies may vary based on website implementation.</em>
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>

    <p>
      We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page 
      with an updated "Last Updated" date.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>

    <p>Questions about cookies or tracking?</p>

    <div class="card">
      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@regume.com">privacy@regume.com</a><br/>
        <strong>Response time:</strong> Within 30 days
      </p>
      <p>
        Read our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for comprehensive information about 
        how we handle your data.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

